Listing information is from various brokers who participate in the Bright MLS IDX program and not all listings may be visible on the site. 
The property information being provided on or through the website is for the personal, non-commercial use of consumers and such information may not be used for any purpose other than to identify prospective properties consumers may be interested in purchasing.

data.description: Great opportunity for this spacious Two Story Brick row located in North Philadelphia. Property features open front porch,  spacious living room, dining room,  kitchen with walk out access to fenced in rear yard. Second floor shows 3 good sizable bedrooms with ample closet space and 3pc. hall bath. Full unfinished basement. Conveniently close to local shopping, schools, transportation and mins. away from major roadway.
